08.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Nation-of-language@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Nation-of-language@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Nation-of-language@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nation-of-language">Nation Of Language</a>分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/darlene-love">Darlene Love</a>的节日经典歌曲“圣诞节（宝贝请回家）”的翻唱 - 请在下面查看。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="656" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nation-of-language-strange-disciple-review-3497127"><b>《语言之国》——《奇怪的门徒》评论：邪教英雄继续他们的热门势头</b></a></li></ul><p>由 Ian Devaney、Aidan Noell 和 Alex MacKay 组成的布鲁克林独立合成流行三重奏为 1963 年的歌曲注入了独特的风格，这首歌曲是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phil-spector">Phil Spector</a>的<i>A Christmas Gift For You</i>合辑中著名的一部分。</p><p> Nation Of Language 与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/u2">U2</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cher">Cher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mariah-carey">Mariah Carey</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/death-cab-for-cutie">Death Cab For Cutie</a>等乐队一起翻唱了这首歌，Spector 还与 Ellie Greenwich 和 Jeff Barry 一起创作了这首歌曲。在这个版本中，乐队为歌曲注入了怪异、宽敞的制作和较慢的节奏，平衡了歌曲苦乐参半的情感内心生活。</p><p>在这里听： </p><p><iframe title="圣诞节（宝贝请回家）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9aLocsOYJa4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这只是最近几周最新发布的圣诞主题专辑： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/laufey-shares-festive-santa-baby-video-with-bill-murray-3808730">Laufey 分享了《Santa Baby》的翻唱</a>，并附有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bill-murray">Bill Murray</a>主演的视频， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charlie-puth-shares-wham-inspired-christmas-single-december-25th-3811146">Charlie Puth 推出了受 Wham! 启发的新单曲《December 25th》</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-v-and-bing-crosby-to-release-era-bridging-duet-of-white-christmas-3810292">BTS 的 V 与 Bing Crosby 庄园合作推出新版本的“白色圣诞节”</a> 。</p><p> Black Star Riders 主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ricky-warwick-shares-heavy-festive-single-all-i-want-for-christmas-is-christmas-with-the-cults-billy-duffy-and-def-leppards-joe-elliott-3810726">Ricky Warwick 也通过“All I Want For Christmas…Is Christmas！”给出了更浓重的节日选择。</a> ，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-cult">The Cult</a>的 Billy Duffy 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/def-leppard">Def Leppard</a>的 Joe Elliott 一起，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jason-kelce-and-stevie-nicks-team-up-to-cover-ron-sexsmiths-maybe-this-christmas-3811222">NFL 明星 Jason Kelce 即将发行整张圣诞专辑</a>，其中包括与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-nicks">Stevie Nicks</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boyz-ii-men">Boyz II Men</a>和他的兄弟 Travis 的合作。</p><p>这首单曲是 Nation Of Language 自 2023 年 9 月发行第三张录音室专辑《Strange Disciple》以来的第一首新音乐。 <i>NME</i><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nation-of-language-strange-disciple-review-3497127">在对该唱片的四星评论中</a>写道：“《Strange Disciple》证明了乐队出道三年来成长迅速。通过他们的第三张专辑，Nation Of Language 证明他们能够在坚持自己的根源的同时扩展他们的听觉想象力。在短短 10 首快速曲目中，纽约乐队证明了他们令人怀念的声音始终更多地是关于未来而不是过去。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-nation-of-languages-eerie-cover-of-darlene-loves-christmas-baby-please-come-home-3811364">《Listen to Nation Of Language》对 Darlene Love 的《Christmas (Baby Please Come Home)》的诡异封面</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
