ize-full wp-post-image" alt="安德烈（André300" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andre-3000">安德烈（André3000）</a>对他对爵士专辑“新蓝色太阳”的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">格莱美</a>提名做出了反应，该专辑被特别选中参加年度专辑类别。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-romy-and-sampha-team-up-to-cover-andre-3000s-me-my-to-bury-your-parents-3598029">听罗米和桑帕团队，涵盖André3000的“ Me＆My（埋葬您的父母）”</a></strong></li></ul><p>在接受<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/11/08/arts/music/andre-3000-grammys-new-blue-sun.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>的采访时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/outkast">Outkast</a>成员 - 真实姓名AndréBenjamin-说，他在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">上周五（11月8日）宣布提名</a>时刚刚醒来。</p><p>他承认：“我们可能会以某种方式提名替代爵士乐或环境。” “但是我对此感到非常惊讶。是的，它是超级，超级，超级傻瓜酷。”</p><p> “ New Blue Sun”是一张乐器爵士专辑，可以看到本杰明表演长笛 - 被提名为年度专辑，最佳替代爵士专辑，以及专辑的开场曲目的最佳乐器作品，“我发誓，我真的很想制作一张“说唱”专辑，但这实际上就是这次风吹吹我的方式。</p><p>这位面试官还向本杰明提到了Outkast的2004年大型巨型专辑“ SpeakerBoxxx/The Love下面”是最终赢得年度专辑的最后一张说唱专辑，他推测“说唱对选民可能并不重要”。</p><p> “我必须说，即使&#39;SpeakerBoxxx/The Love下面&#39;是最后一张说唱专辑，但这是一张说唱专辑。因此，即使在那说，这就是我们的享受，而不是说唱。” </p><figure id="attachment_3789267" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3789267" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3789267" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns.jpg" alt="Andre 3000在挪威奥斯陆的2024年2024年演出。学分：Per Ole Hagen/Redferns" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Andre-3000-performs-at-Oyafestivalen-2024-in-Oslo-Norway.-CREDIT_-Per-Ole-Hagen_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3789267" class="wp-caption-text"> Andre 3000在挪威奥斯陆的2024年2024年演出。学分：Per Ole Hagen/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>本杰明（Benjamin）与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯（Beyoncé</a> ），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比利·埃里什（Billie Eilish）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">查理（Charli XCX</a> ），雅各布·科利尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jacob-collier">（Jacob Collier）</a> ，萨布丽娜·卡彭特<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">（Sabrina Carpenter）和泰勒·斯威夫特</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">Taylor Swift）</a>一起被提名为颁奖典礼的顶级专辑奖。请参阅<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">此处</a>的提名完整列表。</p><p>八月，本杰明分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-andre-3000s-new-album-film-listening-to-the-sun-3789263"><em>听太阳的聆听</em></a>，这是一种完整的视觉效果，其中包含“新蓝色太阳”的音乐 - 它看到安德烈（André）在他的专辑中深深地沉浸在一个神秘的蓝色房间中。</p><p>今年早些时候，本杰明<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-explains-why-he-stopped-rapping-3542363">（</a> Benjamin以这种方式谈论的任何事情。我今年48岁了。并不是说年龄是决定您说唱的事情，而是在某种程度上做到了。”</p><p>这是一条评论，引发了说唱界的争议，其中那些对自己的决定感到沮丧的人， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-on-ll-cool-j-telling-him-to-rap-again-im-not-trying-to-uphold-a-thing-ive-done-before-3775495">ll cool J</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ja-rule">Ja Rule</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/killer-mike-responds-andre-3000-too-old-to-rap-2024-grammys-3582144">Killer Mike</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lil-wayne">Lil Wayne</a> 。后者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-wayne-its-so-depressing-that-andre-3000-said-hes-too-old-to-rap-3552410">说，这“令人沮丧”，安德烈3000感到“老了”，无法说唱</a>，而Ja Rule <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ja-rule-heartbroken-by-andre-3000-not-wanting-to-rap-anymore-lil-wayne-3574948">说他“伤心欲绝”，因为专辑中包含“ No Bars”</a> 。</p><p>最近，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-announces-intimate-londons-jazz-cafe-performances-ahead-of-all-points-east-3779226">在伦敦举行了亲密的演出</a>，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-divides-fans-with-flute-performance-at-all-points-east-3784852">在东方的所有角度进行了分裂的表现</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-reacts-to-grammy-nominations-for-flute-album-new-blue-sun-i-was-totally-surprised-by-this-3811300">André3000邮报对长笛专辑“ New Blue Sun”的提名作出了反应：“我对此感到非常惊讶”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
